1972;;Adolf Hitler: My Part in his Downfall;;British;;Norman Cohen;;Jim Dale, Arthur Lowe, Spike Milligan;;comedy;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adolf_Hitler:_My_Part_in_his_Downfall_(film);;Aspiring jazz musician Terence "Spike" Milligan reluctantly obeys his call-up and joins the Royal Artillery regiment at Bexhill-on-Sea, where he begins training to take part in World War II. But along the way Spike and his friends get involved in many amusing - and some not-so amusing - scrapes.